            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Cover the <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>until flattened to approx. 1cm thickness</p><p>Season the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and coat in <strong>half</strong> your <strong>curry powder </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
