          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick, with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to a plate and set aside, these will finish cooking in the sauce later (reserve the pan!)</p>",
