      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, top your <strong>warmed brioche bun base</strong> with some of the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>tomato slices</strong>,<strong> chicken &</strong> <strong>korma sauce</strong> and the<strong> warmed brioche bun lid</strong> – this is your <strong>chicken korma burger</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>remaining salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
